import React from 'react';
import { 
    Box, 
    Container, 
    Grid, 
    Card, 
    CardContent,
    Typography,
    IconButton,
    Tooltip,
    Paper
} from '@mui/material';
import AddIcon from '@mui/icons-material/Add';
import CalendarTodayIcon from '@mui/icons-material/CalendarToday';
import SchoolIcon from '@mui/icons-material/School';
import AssignmentIcon from '@mui/icons-material/Assignment';
import SmartToyIcon from '@mui/icons-material/SmartToy';

function Dashboard() {
    return (
        <Box
            sx={{
                minHeight: 'calc(100vh - 64px)',
                background: 'linear-gradient(135deg, #0A0A0F 0%, #1a1a1f 100%)',
                py: 6,
                position: 'relative',
                '&::before': {
                    content: '""',
                    position: 'absolute',
                    top: 0,
                    right: 0,
                    bottom: 0,
                    left: 0,
                    background: 'radial-gradient(circle at 50% 0%, rgba(220, 20, 60, 0.1) 0%, transparent 50%)',
                    pointerEvents: 'none'
                }
            }}
        >
            <Container maxWidth="xl">
                <Grid container spacing={4}>
                    {/* Class Schedule Section */}
                    <Grid item xs={12} md={6}>
                        <Card
                            sx={{
                                height: '100%',
                                background: 'rgba(17, 17, 17, 0.6)',
                                backdropFilter: 'blur(20px)',
                                borderRadius: 3,
                                border: '1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1)',
                                transition: 'transform 0.2s ease-in-out, box-shadow 0.2s ease-in-out',
                                '&:hover': {
                                    transform: 'translateY(-4px)',
                                    boxShadow: '0 8px 24px rgba(220, 20, 60, 0.2)',
                                    '& .add-button': {
                                        opacity: 1,
                                    }
                                }
                            }}
                        >
                            <CardContent sx={{ height: '100%', p: 3 }}>
                                <Box sx={{ display: 'flex', justifyContent: 'space-between', alignItems: 'center', mb: 3 }}>
                                    <Typography variant="h6" sx={{ 
                                        display: 'flex', 
                                        alignItems: 'center', 
                                        gap: 1.5,
                                        color: 'rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.9)',
                                        fontWeight: 500
                                    }}>
                                        <SchoolIcon sx={{ color: '#DC143C' }} />
                                        Class Schedule
                                    </Typography>
                                    <Tooltip title="Add Class">
                                        <IconButton 
                                            className="add-button"
                                            sx={{ 
                                                color: '#DC143C',
                                                opacity: 0.7,
                                                transition: 'opacity 0.2s ease-in-out',
                                                '&:hover': {
                                                    background: 'rgba(220, 20, 60, 0.1)',
                                                }
                                            }}
                                        >
                                            <AddIcon />
                                        </IconButton>
                                    </Tooltip>
                                </Box>
                                <Paper
                                    sx={{
                                        p: 4,
                                        background: 'rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.03)',
                                        borderRadius: 2,
                                        textAlign: 'center',
                                        border: '1px dashed rgba(220, 20, 60, 0.3)',
                                        cursor: 'pointer',
                                        transition: 'all 0.2s ease-in-out',
                                        '&:hover': {
                                            background: 'rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.05)',
                                            border: '1px dashed rgba(220, 20, 60, 0.5)',
                                        }
                                    }}
                                >
                                    <Typography color="text.secondary" sx={{ fontSize: '0.95rem' }}>
                                        Add your class schedule to get started
                                    </Typography>
                                </Paper>
                            </CardContent>
                        </Card>
                    </Grid>

                    {/* Exam Dates Section */}
                    <Grid item xs={12} md={6}>
                        <Card
                            sx={{
                                height: '100%',
                                background: 'rgba(17, 17, 17, 0.6)',
                                backdropFilter: 'blur(20px)',
                                borderRadius: 3,
                                border: '1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1)',
                                transition: 'transform 0.2s ease-in-out, box-shadow 0.2s ease-in-out',
                                '&:hover': {
                                    transform: 'translateY(-4px)',
                                    boxShadow: '0 8px 24px rgba(220, 20, 60, 0.2)',
                                    '& .add-button': {
                                        opacity: 1,
                                    }
                                }
                            }}
                        >
                            <CardContent sx={{ height: '100%', p: 3 }}>
                                <Box sx={{ display: 'flex', justifyContent: 'space-between', alignItems: 'center', mb: 3 }}>
                                    <Typography variant="h6" sx={{ 
                                        display: 'flex', 
                                        alignItems: 'center', 
                                        gap: 1.5,
                                        color: 'rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.9)',
                                        fontWeight: 500
                                    }}>
                                        <CalendarTodayIcon sx={{ color: '#DC143C' }} />
                                        Exam Dates
                                    </Typography>
                                    <Tooltip title="Add Exam">
                                        <IconButton 
                                            className="add-button"
                                            sx={{ 
                                                color: '#DC143C',
                                                opacity: 0.7,
                                                transition: 'opacity 0.2s ease-in-out',
                                                '&:hover': {
                                                    background: 'rgba(220, 20, 60, 0.1)',
                                                }
                                            }}
                                        >
                                            <AddIcon />
                                        </IconButton>
                                    </Tooltip>
                                </Box>
                                <Paper
                                    sx={{
                                        p: 4,
                                        background: 'rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.03)',
                                        borderRadius: 2,
                                        textAlign: 'center',
                                        border: '1px dashed rgba(220, 20, 60, 0.3)',
                                        cursor: 'pointer',
                                        transition: 'all 0.2s ease-in-out',
                                        '&:hover': {
                                            background: 'rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.05)',
                                            border: '1px dashed rgba(220, 20, 60, 0.5)',
                                        }
                                    }}
                                >
                                    <Typography color="text.secondary" sx={{ fontSize: '0.95rem' }}>
                                        Add your upcoming exams
                                    </Typography>
                                </Paper>
                            </CardContent>
                        </Card>
                    </Grid>

                    {/* Tasks Section */}
                    <Grid item xs={12} md={6}>
                        <Card
                            sx={{
                                height: '100%',
                                background: 'rgba(17, 17, 17, 0.6)',
                                backdropFilter: 'blur(20px)',
                                borderRadius: 3,
                                border: '1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1)',
                                transition: 'transform 0.2s ease-in-out, box-shadow 0.2s ease-in-out',
                                '&:hover': {
                                    transform: 'translateY(-4px)',
                                    boxShadow: '0 8px 24px rgba(220, 20, 60, 0.2)',
                                    '& .add-button': {
                                        opacity: 1,
                                    }
                                }
                            }}
                        >
                            <CardContent sx={{ height: '100%', p: 3 }}>
                                <Box sx={{ display: 'flex', justifyContent: 'space-between', alignItems: 'center', mb: 3 }}>
                                    <Typography variant="h6" sx={{ 
                                        display: 'flex', 
                                        alignItems: 'center', 
                                        gap: 1.5,
                                        color: 'rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.9)',
                                        fontWeight: 500
                                    }}>
                                        <AssignmentIcon sx={{ color: '#DC143C' }} />
                                        Tasks
                                    </Typography>
                                    <Tooltip title="Add Task">
                                        <IconButton 
                                            className="add-button"
                                            sx={{ 
                                                color: '#DC143C',
                                                opacity: 0.7,
                                                transition: 'opacity 0.2s ease-in-out',
                                                '&:hover': {
                                                    background: 'rgba(220, 20, 60, 0.1)',
                                                }
                                            }}
                                        >
                                            <AddIcon />
                                        </IconButton>
                                    </Tooltip>
                                </Box>
                                <Paper
                                    sx={{
                                        p: 4,
                                        background: 'rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.03)',
                                        borderRadius: 2,
                                        textAlign: 'center',
                                        border: '1px dashed rgba(220, 20, 60, 0.3)',
                                        cursor: 'pointer',
                                        transition: 'all 0.2s ease-in-out',
                                        '&:hover': {
                                            background: 'rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.05)',
                                            border: '1px dashed rgba(220, 20, 60, 0.5)',
                                        }
                                    }}
                                >
                                    <Typography color="text.secondary" sx={{ fontSize: '0.95rem' }}>
                                        Add tasks to optimize your study schedule
                                    </Typography>
                                </Paper>
                            </CardContent>
                        </Card>
                    </Grid>

                    {/* AI Study Assistant Section */}
                    <Grid item xs={12} md={6}>
                        <Card
                            sx={{
                                height: '100%',
                                background: 'rgba(17, 17, 17, 0.6)',
                                backdropFilter: 'blur(20px)',
                                borderRadius: 3,
                                border: '1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1)',
                                transition: 'transform 0.2s ease-in-out, box-shadow 0.2s ease-in-out',
                                '&:hover': {
                                    transform: 'translateY(-4px)',
                                    boxShadow: '0 8px 24px rgba(220, 20, 60, 0.2)',
                                    '& .add-button': {
                                        opacity: 1,
                                    }
                                }
                            }}
                        >
                            <CardContent sx={{ height: '100%', p: 3 }}>
                                <Box sx={{ display: 'flex', justifyContent: 'space-between', alignItems: 'center', mb: 3 }}>
                                    <Typography variant="h6" sx={{ 
                                        display: 'flex', 
                                        alignItems: 'center', 
                                        gap: 1.5,
                                        color: 'rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.9)',
                                        fontWeight: 500
                                    }}>
                                        <SmartToyIcon sx={{ color: '#DC143C' }} />
                                        AI Study Assistant
                                    </Typography>
                                    <Tooltip title="Start Chat">
                                        <IconButton 
                                            className="add-button"
                                            sx={{ 
                                                color: '#DC143C',
                                                opacity: 0.7,
                                                transition: 'opacity 0.2s ease-in-out',
                                                '&:hover': {
                                                    background: 'rgba(220, 20, 60, 0.1)',
                                                }
                                            }}
                                        >
                                            <SmartToyIcon />
                                        </IconButton>
                                    </Tooltip>
                                </Box>
                                <Paper
                                    sx={{
                                        p: 4,
                                        background: 'rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.03)',
                                        borderRadius: 2,
                                        textAlign: 'center',
                                        border: '1px dashed rgba(220, 20, 60, 0.3)',
                                        cursor: 'pointer',
                                        transition: 'all 0.2s ease-in-out',
                                        '&:hover': {
                                            background: 'rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.05)',
                                            border: '1px dashed rgba(220, 20, 60, 0.5)',
                                        }
                                    }}
                                >
                                    <Typography color="text.secondary" sx={{ fontSize: '0.95rem' }}>
                                        Get personalized study plans and assistance
                                    </Typography>
                                </Paper>
                            </CardContent>
                        </Card>
                    </Grid>
                </Grid>
            </Container>
        </Box>
    );
}

export default Dashboard;
